  "notes": "This plan is focused on secure, production-grade email/password authentication. Lucia Auth is used for modern, type-safe authentication. All endpoints are validated with Zod, and security best practices (rate limiting, CORS, helmet) are enforced. The architecture is modular and testable, with clear separation of concerns. The project is ready for future extensibility (RBAC, OAuth, etc.) and can be deployed with Docker and monitored in production."
